data.alt: A capybara sitting and facing the camera directly. An Among Us crew member outline is drawn crudely around the capybara's silhouette.
An adult capybara "booping" (bumping) a baby capybara from behind. Both are in shallow water.
A capybara rides on another capybara's back in a body of water.
A capybara wearing a blue hat is in a field of purple flowers.
A capybara standing in profile in front of a black background. The picture is cropped so that only the front half is visible.
Two capybaras looking toward the upper right corner of the frame
A capybara looking directly at the camera. The capybara is sitting on a dirt field
A hairy capybara being groomed by a pack of small primates. THe capybara's eyes are closed and is sitting on a mossy field
An adult capybara and four capybara pups sitting on a muddy bank by a body of water. They are all looking at something behind and to the right of the frame.
A capybara sitting by a metal fence. A pony is nuzzling it from behind.
A capybara wearing a blue hat is in a field of purple flowers, looking up at the camera.
A long shot of a capybara chewing grass in a green field.
A capybara with its eyes closed lying on a grey pillow with a dozen or so ducklings hanging out with it
A meme image asking Why do we have hands? It says to pat the capy, hold the capy, cherish the capy, and forfeit all mortal possessions to capy
A capybara lying on a muddy bank. A black bird is perched on its shoulder
A capybara eating a watermelon
A baby capybara wearing a batman shirt
A capybara sleeping on a grey pillow with some ducklings
A capybara on its hind legs
A capybara standing on a rainy street.
A capybara lying on its side on grass. It seems to be in the middle of rolling over
A medium shot of a capybara's head. A grey and yellow bird is perched behind its ears
A painting of a capybara
Three capybaras sitting close together on sandy ground, backs toward the camera.
a large group of at least seven capybaras taken with a wide angle lens. They are all eating a pumpkin in the center of the frame.
